import PyPDF2

pdf_path = './15-EmpathyBias/EmpathyBias-main/paper.pdf'
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(pdf_path)
num_pages = len(reader.pages)

# Read the first 5 pages for context
paper_text = ''
for i in range(min(5, num_pages)):
    paper_text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

print(paper_text[:2000])  # Print the first 2000 characters for inspection
